{"tid":211033,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[強國劇] 有冇人睇擇天記","createTime":"2017-04-21T10:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T02:25:25.000Z","uid":87108,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc856cc0ffc08ce23ef6f7bb83702d397fd8f7e8","tid":211033,"uid":87108,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:52:22.000Z","msg":"小說改編，有獎門人同張兆輝　今個禮拜一開始做<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.ijq.tv/201704/11/14-41-23-78-26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.ijq.tv%2F201704%2F11%2F14-41-23-78-26.jpg&h=8e15820e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獎門人<br />\n<br />\n首先有睇過原著小說同期望佢跟原著拍既可以唔洗睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n劇情改到七彩，人物背景就基本一樣<br />\n選角我覺得男女主角都唔差既，典型泡仔樣同范冰冰整容樣<br />\n不過劇情搞到男主角中左化骨綿掌咁算點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電腦特技就假左Ｄ，劇情因為睇過小說既關係所以一路睇一路屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇未睇過原著既巴打有睇，覺得點？<br />\n先入為主睇到好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5a8d8ed67426cf15883180c35f3b1732d1268c","tid":211033,"uid":102134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:53:28.000Z","msg":"獎門人做計道人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd9f6c1715b44b0cc81b1962c8c242787596001","tid":211033,"uid":87108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.ijq.tv/201703/31/10-23-13-60-26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.ijq.tv%2F201703%2F31%2F10-23-13-60-26.jpg&h=2b5b356f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張兆輝"},{"pid":"760731e6e52c3f6345aa7c25e2e86ae71f57fa31","tid":211033,"uid":87108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>獎門人做計道人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，性格完全同書入面相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s